Summary: At work came out of one building happen to look up and saw 3 objects.
divs: Sighting DetailsLooked up after exiting a shop building at work, I looked up at one of our towers at work and high above I saw 3 white what I thought to be birds but as I watch they wher to high up in the sky, and traveling to fast. I only had about 10 sec. To observe them but I quickly saw them in formation keeping pace together. Birds have a lag time to flap their wings in which case they'd fall back alittle. This was my first experience very exciting.
